text: KING-LP (95.1 FM), is an American low-power FM radio station broadcasting a religious format. Licensed to Lusk, Wyoming, the station is currently owned by New Life in Christ Baptist Church. ==References== ==External links== * ING-LP ING-LP Category:Niobrara County, Wyoming Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Wyoming ING-LP Category:Baptist organizations in the United States
